@NotNull java.lang.String formatShortFormTime(long time)
        Formats the given time in short-form.
        This method will calculate to make sure that the formatted time is shortest. For instance, only seconds is displayed if the given time is below 60 seconds. Or if the given time is below 60 minutes, the hour will be hidden
        Parameters:

        Returns:
